◆ cmdCallback()

def modee_node.ModEE.cmdCallback (   self,
  data 
)

subscribe command which modee will do

Parameters
[in]dataros Int16MultiArray message
- data[0] is command
command is listed like below
0: Waiting, modee will wait for command
1: Feedback Control, modee will do feedback control with this command
2: Aspirating, modee will do aspirating with this command
3: Dispensing, modee will do dispensing with this command
4: Pumping, modee will do pumping with this command
5: stop, modee will stop both actuators(vertical motion unit actuator and rotary motion unit actuator) with this command


- data[1] is goal volume for feedback control

Note
input constraints:
- command should be ranged from 0 to 5
- goal volume should be ranged from 0 to 100

◆ feedback_control_process()

def modee_node.ModEE.feedback_control_process (   self,
  goal_vol = -1 
)

feedback control to adjust micropipette volume

feedback control would be processed like bellow
- process 0: move to present volume
- process 1: feedback control with difference of goal volume and present volume.
if the difference is bigger than 10, it will rotated with XX acceleration and XX velocity
if the difference is bigger than 3, it will rotated with XX acceleration and XX velocity
if the difference is less than 3, it will rotated with XX acceleration and XX velocity
- process 2: feedback control to adjust differnce of center percentage less than 10 percent

Parameters
[in]goal_volgoal volume
Note
input constraints:
- goal volume should be ranged from 0 to 100
Returns
result: result of the process
